{"tid":953983,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"求名搵H漫","createTime":"2018-12-24T10:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T08:36:30.000Z","uid":68051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ddd2c971328bb647919f7cc61756a42a747447","tid":953983,"uid":68051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"套h漫講男主角有個同父異母定同同母異父嘅家姐，雖然得返佢兩個一齊住，但男主角就唔係太鍾意佢家姐。<br />\n<br />\n咁有一次唔記得點解就扑左佢家姐，之後仲調教佢，有次佢哋表姐去佢地屋企食飯，個家姐就俾主角用震蛋整到煮煮下飯高潮暈左，跟住表姐知道左佢哋嘅關係，仲同主角搞埋一份。<br />\n<br />\n有次主角好似同佢表姐喺公園搞，俾佢條女撞見。佢條女為左箍住主角就話要同主角結婚，但條女好似唔知男主角同佢家姐嘅事，最尾嗰幕就係個家姐喺男主角去渡蜜月前一晚幫男主角含，話要喺主角渡蜜月前吸乾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知喺邊套或者佢乜嘢名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a22a57be50cdfb717c70588b68a4a11232d8238","tid":953983,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"61ae52a55690ce98c678032da7dda0d92945509a","tid":953983,"uid":68051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a0cb6b0bfeac3ff273612f7dc149ea63ed887b","tid":953983,"uid":68051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ef7b9d4b0e3ac54c3a05b132ab32bdea75b263","tid":953983,"uid":115250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c241kbO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc241kbO.gif&h=fe11d845&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c37c77bd904ff0dfb4177bb597652c25a69d2c8","tid":953983,"uid":37067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:36:30.000Z","msg":"搵咗半年?"}]}